{
  "stem": "14900.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I think maybe there was a chamber pot in there in a corner.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Get some fresh air-- one at a time we'd go back in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "After more than a week-- I know that-- a young man came and it was at a different time, and we thought we were found, that our hiding place had been discovered.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He was a messenger.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Our friend had sent him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The Germans had promised they were now totally liquidating the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The name Rumkowski, who was the president of the ghetto and the government, had agreed to leave on a passenger train that was being provided for them, the factory heads, the police, and their families, whoever was left in the ghetto-- safe transport to Germany to work in a factory.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The message was they had accepted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "If we wanted to continue hiding there would be no one to help us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So we all decided to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "As soon as we reached the train station [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we knew it was wrong.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "SS officers, police dogs, billy clubs, sub machine guns, cattle train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They forced aboard this train, probably 100 people in each car.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "There was no room to stretch your legs out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "You could sit down almost in a fetal position, like this, curled up, your feet under you, then the next person, the next.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Well, by then I was 14 and I had a very good, straight upbringing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I had become the provider and the procurer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So I managed to quickly get a little area against one of the walls of the car so at least we had something to lean against.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And my mother and I sat down there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "One more time, the same scenario-- slam the doors, lock 'em, off we went.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
